OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry, but often cloudy morning,
OL,6,Fwith a few brighter or sunny spells.
OL,7,FCloud clearing in the afternoon to
OL,8,Fgive longer sunny periods. Moderate
OL,9,Fwinds but feeling mild.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FClear skies to start before
OL,12,Flow cloud and fog patches move slowly
OL,13,Fnorthwards across the region
OL,14,Fovernight. Remaining relatively mild.
OL,15,
OL,16,CWednesday:FMorning fog and low cloud
OL,17,Fwill lift to give a dry and very day,
OL,18,Fwith brighter spells, but remaining
OL,19,Fcloudier to the northwest.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
